snippet.title: Zueirama 2077
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/952290/Zueirama/
The year is 2077, my city has become the craziest place in the world.
Main issues?
Memes, trolls and jurry-rig everywhere.
The city is full of opportunities for Trolling, and I am BIG Troll.
Discover the power of the zueira.
Available now on Steam
